// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/lXfyWN spheres and tori wave grid exact, 2024 by jt
// combines https://www.shadertoy.com/view/lXXyD4 unit cube intersect sphere exact
// with https://www.shadertoy.com/view/M3XyWN unit cube intersects torus exact
// using https://www.shadertoy.com/view/DdX3z4 euclidean distance sdf debugger

// Exact euclidean sdf of hills and valleys formed by spheres and tori.

// TODO: Can this be parametrized?

// tags: sdf, torus, cube, sphere, intersection, distance, debug, intersect, euclidean, and, unit, exact, hill, valley, debugger

